             was indicted for <rs id="t18340904-8-off47" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340904-8-off47" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340904-8-off47" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18340904-8-cd48" type="crimeDate">5th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340904-8-off47 t18340904-8-cd48"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340904-8-off49 t18340904-8-cd48"></join>, at St. Luke's, 2 coats, value 3l. 10s.; 1 pair of trowsers, value 15s.; 2 waistcoats, value 8s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18340904-8-victim164" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Brown
                     <interp inst="t18340904-8-victim164" type="surname" value="Brown"></interp>
